ActDepartment of Veterans Affairs Act
Canadian Forces Members and Veterans Re-establishment and Compensation Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Veterans Health Care Regulations and the Canadian Forces Members and Veterans Re-establishment and Compensation Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the VETERANS HEALTH CARE REGULATIONS AND THE CANADIAN FORCES MEMBERS AND VETERANS RE-ESTABLISHMENT AND COMPENSATION REGULATIONS in order to (1) eliminate duplication in the types of benefits and services for serving Canadian forces members; (2) change the career transition services delivery model for veterans and survivors; and (3) address items raised by the Standing Joint Committee on Scrutiny of Regulations.
